{"tid":2166101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【左膠國立法】狗主每日必須帶狗出街兩次，每次必須一個鐘以上！","createTime":"2020-08-20T08:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T23:31:45.000Z","uid":193077,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b0035feb36243261ba073306cd33fa47c582dbca","tid":2166101,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"德國農業部長克勒克納（Julia Klockner）表示，政府將在《犬隻法案》（Dogs Act）中加入新規例，要求養狗人士每天必須遛狗兩次，每次必須有一小時或以上，原因是該國940萬隻寵物狗中，許多沒有得到牠們所需要的鍛煉或刺激。"},{"pid":"ec2bdee07dfc63a626ed3cf825cfccfe0ba4f19b","tid":2166101,"uid":193077,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"左膠大國名不虛傳"},{"pid":"560d97b7b9fdeed3ed4cfdd82153c6fb94d7345d","tid":2166101,"uid":328232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"err... 瑞典係要每日4次。所以周圍都有勁多狗托兒所 (Hundsdaggis)"},{"pid":"2e70bfcdea0fb5488bec21358c85d77f5be725c6","tid":2166101,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"560d97b7b9fdeed3ed4cfdd82153c6fb94d7345d","tid":2166101,"uid":328232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"err... 瑞典係要每日4次。所以周圍都有勁多狗托兒所 (Hundsdaggis)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:29:38.000Z","msg":"另一個左膠國"},{"pid":"17ba788d8dc1d7c6fa9d630e926399d8244a25d4","tid":2166101,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"美國幫人放狗人工好似都唔錯"},{"pid":"0a5c1d8b430f09a076cd444a61e2b604f91312c1","tid":2166101,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:30:54.000Z","msg":"許多沒有得到牠們所需要的鍛煉或<span class=\"red\">刺激</span><br />\n<br />\n乜嘢刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3197bc5dd01b03949318bceaa486cd2255c6a522","tid":2166101,"uid":164124,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":